== Party System Overview ==

Dragon Warrior IV uses a unique chapter-based system where players control different characters throughout the game. Each chapter focuses on different party members with their own storylines.

=== Chapter Structure ===

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Chapter !! Playable Characters !! Notes
|-
| 1 || Ragnar || Solo quest with temporary helper
|-
| 2 || Alena, Cristo, Brey || Three-person party
|-
| 3 || Taloon || Solo merchant adventure
|-
| 4 || Mara, Nara || Sister duo quest
|-
| 5 || Hero + All others || Full party assembled
|}

